    <string name="app_description">
        In most peoples day-to-day life they perform repetitive and seemingly pointless tasks, I\'m sure that you
        can relate. Repetitive tasks that we have grown to think that we like, things that take up a lot of our time
        but don\'t add anything to our lives.
        \n\nThe things that we won\'t remember when we grow old.
        \n\nI think that most people don\'t even appreciate these parts of their lives, but it\'s not easy to find an
        option of doing something more exciting, something that would be worth remembering.
        \n\nThis is my attempt of giving you that option.
    </string>
